- **[MODIFY] [settings/page.tsx](file:///d:/Nisarg.Doc/Skaps/chatbot/src/app/admin/settings/page.tsx)**:
  - Added a stateful **Allowed LLM Models** management interface inside the **AI / LLM Settings** section.
