## Technical Flow Overview

The model availability pipeline works seamlessly:

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Admin Panel (Settings)
    participant Client as User Chat Panel
    participant Backend as FastAPI Backend
    participant Studio as LM Studio (/v1/models)

    Admin->>Backend: GET /chat/models
    Backend->>Studio: Fetch loaded model IDs
    Note over Backend,Studio: Intersect loaded models with DB llm_models list
    Backend-->>Admin: Return model status list
    Note over Admin: Render active (green) and inactive (gray) badges

    Client->>Backend: GET /chat/models
    Backend-->>Client: Return only active models
    Note over Client: Populate ChatInput select with active models

    Client->>Backend: POST /chat/send (includes model)
    Backend->>Studio: ask_lm_studio(..., model=chosen)
    Backend-->>Client: Return answer & persist model in ChatMessage
```

